Long Island Rail Road Reports Some Services Suspended on Signal Problems

-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 
2011-09-29T21:06:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/long-island-rail-road-suspends-some-trains-on-rain-related-signal-problems.html
Long Island Rail Road said service
is temporarily suspended in both directions between  Penn Station 
and  Jamaica  and between Atlantic Terminal and Jamaica, because
of weather-related signal trouble.  The agency commented on its website.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
 gchang1@bloomberg.net  